==TheHandi-Van==
TheHandi-Van是檀香山巴士的辅助巴士系统，用于服务那些无法使用普通巴士的残障人士。乘客需要提前预约该种巴士<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.honolulu.gov/dts/riders.htm |title = Handi-Van Rider's Guide, Official Web Site for The City and County of Honolulu |accessdate = 2008-07-07 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080509194426/http://www.honolulu.gov/dts/riders.htm |archivedate = 2008-05-09 }}</ref>，而该车队共有160辆巴士<ref name="TheBusFY12-13">{{cite web| author=City and County of Honolulu department of Transit Services/Oahu Transit Services| title=TheBus Fast Facts| date=Fiscal Year 2012-2013| publisher=City and County of Honolulu department of Transit Services/Oahu Transit Services| url=http://www.thebus.org/AboutTheBus/TheBusFacts.pdf| page=2| format=PDF| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120710200254/http://www.thebus.org/AboutTheBus/TheBusFacts.pdf| archivedate=2012-07-10}}</ref>。

==营运车辆==
2012至2013财年，巴士公司共有各类客车518辆，其中[[铰接客车|铰接客车]]111量，40英尺标准巴士374辆以及小型巴士33辆。其中[[油电混合车|油电混合车]]型的比例为15.4%，车辆平均使用年龄为9.1年<ref name="TheBusFY12-13"/>。所有巴士上的自动语音报站系统均由夏威夷作曲家和语言学家普阿基诺杰梅尔提供原声<ref>{{cite journal| last=Blair| first=Chad| title=Found in Translation| publisher=Hana Hou!| date=February/March 2007| journal=Hana Hou!| volume=10| issue=1| location=Honolulu| url=http://www.hanahou.com/pages/Magazine.asp?Action=DrawArticle&ArticleID=547&MagazineID=34| accessdate=2009-01-13| archive-date=2016-11-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108090842/http://hanahou.com/pages/Magazine.asp?Action=DrawArticle&ArticleID=547&MagazineID=34| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

